---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Sarakpy Ny">
  <section class="page">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <div class="content">
      <p>
        I am a Master's student in Data Science, Statistics, and Machine
        Learning at
        <a
          href="https://www.ensae.fr/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          ENSAE Paris,
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.ip-paris.fr/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Institut Polytechnique de Paris
        </a>. Before that, I studied applied mathematics and statistics at the
        <a href="https://itc.edu.kh/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Institute of Technology of Cambodia.
        </a>
      </p>

      <p>
        My work has combined applied data science and research-oriented machine
        learning. Through internships and academic projects, I have worked on
        recommendation systems, energy performance prediction, financial data
        analysis, sequence models, fairness in machine learning, natural
        language processing, and scientific machine learning.
      </p>

      <p>
        I am currently doing an internship at
        <a
          href="https://www.imt-atlantique.fr/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          IMT Atlantique
        </a>
        in collaboration with
        <a
          href="https://www.inria.fr/en/odyssey"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          INRIA Odyssey,
        </a> where I work on active learning methods for the correction of numerical
        models.
      </p>

      <p>
        More broadly, I am interested in machine learning, statistical learning,
        and scientific modeling, especially in settings where theory,
        computation, and real-world applications meet.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .content p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .content a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
